### LabVerse Android App - Paper API Test Suite
### Base URL: http://10.0.2.2:8080/paper-service/papers/
### Note: 10.0.2.2 is the Android emulator's alias for localhost

@baseUrl = http://10.0.2.2:8080/paper-service/papers
@contentType = application/json

### Variables
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@paperId = YOUR_PAPER_ID_HERE

### 1. Get Paper Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/details?id={{paperId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. Get Citations of Paper
GET {{baseUrl}}/citation?id={{paperId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 3. Get All Papers (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/all?search=machine%20learning&index=0&size=10
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 4. Get All Papers (no search)
GET {{baseUrl}}/all?index=0&size=20
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 5. Delete Paper
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{paperId}}
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

